org.wise.portal.domain.group

Interface Group

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Group>, Persistable, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PersistentGroup

    public interface Group
extends Persistable, Comparable<Group>
    An interface that defines the concept of a group that can be nested in a hierarchy. Group objects are nodes in a group tree hierarchy. Leaf nodes in the tree contain a list of members.
    Author:
    Cynick Young
